Virtual Environment RemoteReps (with all the dependencies installed)
install the redis server
activate the virtual environment RemoteReps
go to the directory scraper
Make Migrations and migrate (py manage.py makemigrations, py manage.py migrate)
Create superuser (py manage.py createsuperuser)
run the server i,e py manage.py runserver
run file scrape\redis=cli.exe
In cmd run the command: "celery -A scraper worker -l info -P eventlet"
Go to the http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin
In Brands section add a company name to search for
In Periodictask tab add a task name as "scraperz" with interval specifications
Then run the selected task.
Go to http://127.0.0.1:8000/
Click on the brand for the list available products
